Missouri_City.KYAZ: KYAZ, virtual channel 51 (UHF digital channel 47), is an Azteca América-affiliated television station serving Houston, Texas, United States that is licensed to Katy. Owned by Northstar Media, LLC, KYAZ maintains studio facilities located at One Arena Place on Bissonnet Street on Houston's southwest side. The transmitter is located near Missouri City, in unincorporated northeastern Fort Bend County.
